      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Stephane Nicolet</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:242px;\"><a href=\"https://www.ffothello.org/idf-5-stephane-nicolet-remporte-le-premier-tournoi-xot-parisien/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/5/53/StephaneNicolet.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"217\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:StephaneNicolet.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Stéphane Nicolet <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Stéphane Nicolet</b>,<br />\na French world-class <a href=\"/Othello\" title=\"Othello\">Othello</a> player, two times <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reversi#World_Othello_Championship\">vice-world champion</a> in 1996 and 2007 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, \ncomputer scientist, teacher and researcher affiliated with <a href=\"/University_of_Paris#2\" title=\"University of Paris\">University of Paris II Panthéon-Assas</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, and computer Othello and chess programmer.\nHe is primary author of the Othello program <i>Cassio</i> for <a href=\"/Macintosh\" title=\"Macintosh\">Macintosh</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. \nIn 2014, Stéphane Nicolet started to work on <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a>, and  became a primary member of the Stockfish community, contributing in all areas with focus on <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">evaluation</a>, <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">tuning</a> and <a href=\"/Engine_Testing\" title=\"Engine Testing\">testing</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2014\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2014</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2015\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2016\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2016</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2017\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2017</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2018\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2018</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2019\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2019</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#2020\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#Stockfish\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Stockfish</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#Othello\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Othello</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-12\"><a href=\"#Cassio\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Cassio</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-13\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stephane_Nicolet&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2014\">2014</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stephane_Nicolet&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2014\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/yInXKtEY2iM/GALcVZp_ULQJ\">An idea for search.cpp&#160;: generalize advanced_pawn_push()</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, January 23, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/peyl4CAsP7M/e_m7rHSSgDgJ\">Something strange in pawns.cpp</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, March 19, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/oJVdjiKWi7k/MUFmCR9OrFgJ\">Help needed&#160;: SPSA session</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, March 25, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/SPSA\" title=\"SPSA\">SPSA</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/of_TQzyz2qo/qVO55TMFJXcJ\">Re: SIMD vector arithmetic</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, April 05, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/ViyAoTA8i4Q/068rdLB9kTgJ\">Hanging pieces patch applied</a> by <a href=\"/Marco_Costalba\" title=\"Marco Costalba\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, April 30, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Hanging_Piece\" title=\"Hanging Piece\">Hanging Piece</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015\">2015</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stephane_Nicolet&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2015\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/4zoh6cxak6k/RySF2o9FAwAJ\">From midgame to endgame: help needed</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, September 17, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Game_Phases\" title=\"Game Phases\">Game Phases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/vGgxv_W_LOI/SAQOxpFsBwAJ\">Komodo, Lazy SMP, and the like&#160;:-)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, September 30, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Komodo\" title=\"Komodo\">Komodo</a>, <a href=\"/Lazy_SMP\" title=\"Lazy SMP\">Lazy SMP</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/Xh8p8KXGrso/aguB__krDAAJ\">Gull's endgame knowledge</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, October 16, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Gull\" title=\"Gull\">Gull</a>, <a href=\"/Rook_Endgame\" title=\"Rook Endgame\">Rook Endgame</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2016\">2016</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stephane_Nicolet&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2016\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/KiqV1h1IBds/_Tn5gPFyBgAJ\">How much would you be ready to give away for a change of ST style&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, June 28, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/rwakDGcuf5E/YUyeJX9rBQAJ\">Two ideas for pawn patches</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, July 28, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Pawn_Rams_(Bitboards)\" title=\"Pawn Rams (Bitboards)\">Pawn Rams (Bitboards)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/_hWkhtPxdDg/ruF0uHjOEAAJ\">A Question about the null move trick</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, August 26, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/9mcmjnyqbAQ/S6mDA0QsAAAJ\">Illegal moves in SEE</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, September 22, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/SEE_-_The_Swap_Algorithm\" title=\"SEE - The Swap Algorithm\">SEE - The Swap Algorithm</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/PsCTdihp9q8/kiy5O480AAAJ\">Github workflow for Stockfish</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, November 19, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/7v29HZhwDsk/DFesjUyZAAAJ\">Some questions about backward pawns</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, November 20, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Backward_Pawn\" title=\"Backward Pawn\">Backward Pawn</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2017\">2017</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stephane_Nicolet&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2017\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/Cbm5y4dpeEE/wYmQokNfAAAJ\">Some data about LazySMP</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, April 08, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Lazy_SMP\" title=\"Lazy SMP\">Lazy SMP</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/AE4EgWQ20dY/d37yA6llBgAJ\">A branch to test the Monte Carlo algorithm in Stockfish</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, December 06, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a>, <a href=\"/AlphaZero\" title=\"AlphaZero\">AlphaZero</a>, <a href=\"/Monte-Carlo_Tree_Search\" title=\"Monte-Carlo Tree Search\">MCTS</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2018\">2018</spa