Draw</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/XnLmUP_78iw/QgMZzmeVBgAJ\">Tuning floats</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, April 12, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/_V1YhOj078g/v_Ff6wGWAQAJ\">Discussion of the cycle detection patch</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, May 17, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/gxAS3isl4pU/FxuoYfo8BQAJ\">Change of maintainer</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, September 03, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/R0ZzvPt81hA/sKei7OsrCwAJ\">How to improve SF rook evaluation?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, October 29, 2018</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2019\">2019</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stephane_Nicolet&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2019\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/PF3dcA8aPh8/hC15Mo2rAwAJ\">TCEC Season 16</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, August 23, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/TCEC_Season_16\" title=\"TCEC Season 16\">TCEC Season 16</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/c4qRQaZKdgU/3FOkhr0XBQAJ\">Congratulations to the new official-stockfish owner, Stéphane Nicolet&#160;!!</a> by asmideus, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, October 21, 2019</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020\">2020</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stephane_Nicolet&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: 2020\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/uJUcbNtnZI4/ztwU3Xw4DQAJ\">Stockfish 11</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, January 18, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72837\">Stockfish 11</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 18, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/nG6aqewRuSM/C5hn5hD3EwAJ\">The Maintainers They Are a-Changin'</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, January 23, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/g/fishcooking/c/5kYNi6H4cCY\">Stepping down</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, June 23, 2021</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">E